(firstQuint)Quality of Life and Sexual Function of the Novasure Endometrial Ablation in Menorrhagia.

 patients diagnosed menorrhagia scheduled for Novasure Endometrial Ablation because of menorrhagia between november, 2012 and november, 2014 are enrolled to this study.

 patients are asked to complete preoperative questionnaires considering Health Related Quality of Life questionnaire(HRQoL) and sexual Female Sexual Functioning Index questionnaire(FSFI).

 Same questionnaires will also be completed six months and one year after operation.

